"pid":"38f17d601f6315051b23477699744d4b0a5bb8b7","tid":973594,"uid":182192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f53dffc325eb37bb76a1d233a1614000d731c1","tid":973594,"uid":65898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"畀左咁多水你國民黨cap，係時候要歸邊啦柒頭"},{"pid":"1665f493a60c48dc548156d165231866e835b80c","tid":973594,"uid":37220,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4a4f8ab764f4aee153381194f34d6c7c0ae02ea8","tid":973594,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"62838a7372647d098f131d71a72a174cf99e6f99","tid":973594,"uid":126731,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a9fa2929ecb58d208175fdd8f753a091795c9099","tid":973594,"uid":37220,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDaBxCK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDaBxCK.jpg&h=da5457fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"打咩臉? 大支那膠乜都醒LA. 2019 LA傻鳩."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:48:40.000Z","msg":"小英無話92有共識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:54:03.000Z","msg":"蔡英文認為未來的台灣人民只有一個選擇 一個中國<br />\n<br />\n點評論"},{"pid":"ca29687f030d680a1411d7f4e4c915c87df3dee0","tid":973594,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"中國93閱兵 連戰坐在天安門城樓第一排<br />\n<br />\n2015-09-03 11:28<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國93閱兵今天登場，國民黨前主席連戰赴中參加，《中評社》拍到連戰與老婆連方瑀坐在天安門城樓第一排觀禮。<br />\n<br />\n連戰赴中國，稱抗戰期間，「中國國民黨軍隊」在蔣介石領導下「正面戰場」重挫日軍，「中國共產黨軍隊」在毛澤東領導下「敵後戰場」牽制日軍，附和中共立場強調國共聯合抗日，連戰也公開呼應中國領導人習近平「兩岸共用史料、共寫史書」的主張，強調「我非常贊同」。<br />\n<br />\n國發會前主委管中閔昨氣得在臉書大罵連戰，「不是東西、丟人現眼、自貶身價」、「你還要去閱兵？閱你個卡蹭（屁股）！」而國民黨台北市議員李新更主張，如果連戰今天堅持登上閱兵台，國民黨至少要做出停權以上處分，「否則難以謝國人！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpmYcuJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpmYcuJg.jpg&h=d9f79961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1432890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1432890&d=4Ag1gy5rOgZ5EjT6Eq90HMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8b2c9f3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1432890&h=7ff392cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1432890</a>"},{"pid":"e4728a1b5c5aa097e15d26faa2a72c5b67472215","tid":973594,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1665f493a60c48dc548156d165231866e835b80c","tid":973594,"uid":37220,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4a4f8ab764f4aee153381194f34d6c7c0ae02ea8","tid":973594,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"62838a7372647d098f131d71a72a174cf99e6f99","tid":973594,"uid":126731,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"打咩臉? 大支那膠乜都醒LA. 2019 LA傻鳩."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:48:40.000Z","msg":"小英無話92有共識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:54:03.000Z","msg":"蔡英文認為未來的台灣人民只有一個選擇 一個中國<br />\n<br />\n點評論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:57:03.000Z","msg":"有幾難評論？本身台灣人就係國民黨餘孽"},{"pid":"f6ed585755cc700232c7a28df126d880bfc9fe22","tid":973594,"uid":23180,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9fa2929ecb58d208175fdd8f753a091795c9099","tid":973594,"uid":37220,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDaBxCK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDaBxCK.jpg&h=da5457fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"其實整呢幅圖果條友有無睇清楚內容<br />\n<br />\n一中同一個中共國係咪無分別?<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文一上台已經好似篇文個內容咁講話歡迎溝通<br />\n<br />\n雜種呢班垃圾除左屌人台獨同用錢引誘台奸之外做過咩???"},{"pid"